headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Hillman (NASDAQ:HLMN) And The Rest Of The Professional Tools and Equipment Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how professional tools and equipment stocks fared in Q4, starting with Hillman (NASDAQ:HLMN).
